
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>My Hometown</title>

    <!-- Internal CSS -->
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #e6f2ff;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        h1 {
            color: darkblue;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 40px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: darkgreen;
        }

        p {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
        }

        img {
            display: block;
            margin: auto;
            border: 3px solid black;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: maroon;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <h1>Welcome to My Hometown</h1>

    <h2>Thiruvananthapuram</h2>

    <!-- Image -->
    <img src=""hometown.jpg" 
          alt="hometown" width="400" height="250">

    <p>
        <span class="highlight">Thiruvananthapuram</span>, the capital city of Kerala, is known for its rich culture, 
        beautiful beaches, and historical landmarks.
    </p>

    <h2>Famous Places</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Padmanabhaswamy Temple</li>
        <li>Kovalam Beach</li>
        <li>Napier Museum</li>
        <li>Zoo and Botanical Garden</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Special Features</h2>
    <p>
        The city is famous for its traditional architecture, festivals, and delicious Kerala cuisine. 
        It is a major center for education and research.
    </p>

    <h2>Culture</h2>
    <p>
        The people here celebrate festivals like <b>Onam</b> and <b>Vishu</b> with great enthusiasm. 
        Classical art forms like Kathakali and Mohiniyattam are also popular.
    </p>

</div>

</body>
</html>
